      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was looking at old photos today. it’s weird. i don't even recognize that person. it feels like that version of me actually died a long time ago... like i'm just some hollow shell walking around, performing the motions of a life that doesn't even belong to me anymore. just a ghost inhabiting a body that's too heavy to carry.",
