      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not even about making a change tho. that's the thing. it's not like i'm stuck in a bad phase. it's more like the \"me\" that was capable of change, of feeling things, of actually living... that's just gone. there's nothing left to fix. it's just this heavy, empty presence that keeps eating up space and resources. it feels so pointless to keep pretending there's a person in here.",
